I"ñ<div style="text-align: justify;"> Working in a pair, we implemented an application for  a <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cave_automatic_virtual_environment" target="_blank">CAVE</a> (Cave automatic virtual environment) and stereoscopic glasses equipped with an eye-tracking system provided by SMI. The goals were to implement a Unity plugin for the glasses and the CAVE, and to use the eye position of the user to reduce motion sickness by blurring everything but  the focus point.</div>
